    <title>Refugees contributor: Giulia McPherson</title>
    <description>Giulia McPherson is the director of advocacy and operations at Jesuit Refugee Service/USA. JRS works in more than 50 countries worldwide to meet the educational, health, psycho-social and emergency needs of refugees and other forcibly displaced persons. She is on Twitter @giuliamcpherson.
</description>
